{"data": {"chapter_num": "6", "title": "世说新语", "author": "蓝雯轩&漫友", "status": "1", "lastTime": "1517814600", "coverImage": "https://ss0.baidu.com/-Po3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy/boxapp_novel/wh%3D315%2C423/sign=8a05bed25ada81cb4eb38bce6353fc22/b58f8c5494eef01f1d424ee3ebfe9925bc317d45.jpg", "horizontalLogo": "", "summary": "一种才情，冠绝古今，仍令人心向往之……那个时代固然动乱，固然有阴霾笼罩，可是那个时代因为一群熠熠生辉的人物而光芒万丈、与众不同。《世说新语•六朝笈》以国学经典名著《世说新语》为蓝本，细腻描绘魏晋名仕的才情傲气，以及为人处世的超然——桓伊为知音而下马踞胡床取笛三弄，不交一言，客主心照不宣；王徽之王献之兄弟情深，一人病逝另一人因为思念竟也不久于世；阮籍苏门寻隐士长啸解愁思，忧虑何解？原来早有人心相知……以漫画的表现方式，再现六朝名仕们的任性与自由，还原那个时代的风土人情，以细腻笔触将他们潇洒背后的凄清寂寞表现得淋漓尽致、直戳人心。！附录古文小剧场，以幽默风趣的方式解读名仕们的轶事。用另一种视角看待魏晋南北朝的时尚和人物“怪异”的行为！坦胸露怀，扪虱而谈，饮酒醉歌，看他们怎样潇洒出一种风尚！", "summaryShort": "", "tags": ["奇幻", "历史", "仙侠"], "cp_name": "爱奇艺漫画", "cp_id": "16", "save_content": "0", "book_ad": "0", "public_status": "0", "allChapterList": [{"book_id": "8590039332", "chapter_id": "1657350", "chapter_index": "1", "raw_chapter_id": "229470170", "chapter_title": "1", "chapter_url": "http://h5.m.iqiyi.com/static/baiduReader/reader?comicId=202760070&partId=229470170", "pic_sum": "18", "free": "1", "purchase": "0"}, {"book_id": "8590039332", "chapter_id": "1657369", "chapter_index": "2", "raw_chapter_id": "229480170", "chapter_title": "2", "chapter_url": "http://h5.m.iqiyi.com/static/baiduReader/reader?comicId=202760070&partId=229480170", "pic_sum": "18", "free": "1", "purchase": "0"}, {"book_id": "8590039332", "chapter_id": "1657388", "chapter_index": "3", "raw_chapter_id": "229490170", "chapter_title": "3", "chapter_url": "http://h5.m.iqiyi.com/static/baiduReader/reader?comicId=202760070&partId=229490170", "pic_sum": "19", "free": "1", "purchase": "0"}, {"book_id": "8590039332", "chapter_id": "1657406", "chapter_index": "4", "raw_chapter_id": "229500170", "chapter_title": "4", "chapter_url": "http://h5.m.iqiyi.com/static/baiduReader/reader?comicId=202760070&partId=229500170", "pic_sum": "18", "free": "1", "purchase": "0"}, {"book_id": "8590039332", "chapter_id": "1657419", "chapter_index": "